        <item>
            <title>WhatsApp 新功能，重要信息置顶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/whatsapp-19/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=whatsapp-19</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/whatsapp-19/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 13:40:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[WhatsApp]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[置顶]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210406</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">WhatsApp 终于都跟随其他通讯软件的步伐，在最近的更新中加入了讯息置顶的功能，方便用家置顶重要信息。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210407 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-13-at-7.28.42-PM-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-13-at-7.28.42-PM-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-13-at-7.28.42-PM-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-13-at-7.28.42-PM-768x430.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-13-at-7.28.42-PM-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-13-at-7.28.42-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲WhatsApp 在最近的更新中加入了讯息置顶的功能</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">更新后，用家可以在 WhatsApp 中，把对话信息置顶，基本上所有信息都可以，包括投票功能、媒体档案及表情符号。用家可以长按 WhatsApp 对话来触发功能，再选择「置顶」的选项，即可把信息署顶。用家可把信息置顶 24 小时、7 日或 30 日，惟暂时 WhatsApp 只限置顶一则信息，如要置顶第二项信息，则要把原有的信息除下。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">至于 WhatsApp 群组亦可使用此功能，群组管理员可选择开放置顶权利给所有成员或只准群组管理员置顶。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/12/12/whatsapp-now-lets-you-pin-messages-in-individual-and-group-chats/?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAENYKB4p_zxlAxap7xX9frSIzNqqhzIYZtdfmktN7DGJAM4iDRZtNnnU0LGOX6Cnrcum3T6VtKCAMtK8lmAxEpbofj5BtDZXt0g1TnNWIY0Jl1Nri84mVRCjG71EKNE0NygYthc5_wOpMO1CzAyupOgivSImzENkV7OHluzWBVes">TechCrunch</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/whatsapp-19/software/">WhatsApp 新功能，重要信息置顶</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
