        <item>
            <title>港铁推信用卡出入闸    12 月 23 日 Visa 率先登场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/visa-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=visa-mtr</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/visa-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 11:32:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mtr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Visa]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港铁]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210340</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">港铁公司今（13 日）公布，将于今年 12 月 23 日起，分阶段推出感应式信用卡乘搭港铁服务，乘客当日起可于特定的闸机使用 Visa 体验新服务出闸，而明年第三季将涵盖更多信用卡作支付。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210345 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今年 12 月 23 日起，分阶段推出感应式信用卡乘搭港铁服务</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">现时港铁重铁网络（机场快线车站除外）每个车站已配备起码两部提供感应式信用卡支付功能的出入闸机，较多旅客使用的车站则会有更多配备。新闸机贴有浅蓝色标示，方便乘客辨认。12 月 23 日起，乘客使用感应式信用卡、扣账卡或载有这两项支付功能的装置如手提电话及智能手表等，在浅蓝色闸机的信用卡读卡器一拍便可出入闸，而可使用新支付功能的闸机亦会陆续增加。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210346 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲每个车站已配备起码两部提供感应式信用卡支付功能的出入闸机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210347 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新闸机贴有浅蓝色标示，方便乘客辨认</p><h2>实试入闸</h2><p>使用 Visa 信用卡及扣账卡出入闸过程简单，基本上与八达通一样，只要将 Visa 信用卡及扣账卡往感应器拍卡，乘客会听到「嘟」一声，闸门打门后，即可出入闸。而拍卡至出入闸时间与八达通相约，一拍即能过闸。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210348 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲拍卡至出入闸时间与八达通相约，一拍即能过闸</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">随著重铁网络的感应式信用卡支付服务接受 Visa 信用卡及扣账卡，全部港铁站客务中心亦已增加电子支付服务。信用卡支付的第二阶段将于二零二四年第三季展开，更多信用卡可作电子支付。公司亦计划最快于二零二六年在机场快线更新闸机，同时提供感应式信用卡付费乘车服务，而整项自动收费系统资产更新计划预计于二零二八年完成，届时港铁网络的闸机会完成全面提升。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210403 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲信用卡支付的第二阶段将于二零二四年第三季展开，更多信用卡可作电子支付。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/visa-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/">港铁推信用卡出入闸    12 月 23 日 Visa 率先登场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
